A_382 - Trees can also be decorated (especially the trunks). Contrary to popular belief, just as aesthetics is important in some cases, improvements can also be achieved by decorating trees. Mainly the initial attachment can be done safely, for example with elastic bands that close with hooks, or in other ways. In this way the growth of the tree is not prevented and for example more or less decorated and colored &ldquo;curtains&rdquo; can be placed.